data.description: Move in ready 4 bed, 2 bath home with a triple attached garage.  You will notice a large foyer with a handy coat and storage niche. The upper level features a large living room, spacious kitchen with newer stainless appliances, dining area offers access to the deck, perfect for grilling and relaxing in your private, fenced yard.  There is a patio area which is wired for a hot tub.   The primary bedroom offers 2 closets and plenty of room for a king bed, and all of your furniture. Full bath with double sinks in the upper-level bath are a bonus. Moving to the lower level you will find a cozy family room with a handsome stone wall and gas fireplace. Ideal for entertaining with ample room for recreation. There are two bedrooms and a ¾ bath, with a newer shower and heated floor.  Note: storage under the steps, and in the laundry / mechanical area. Great Hilltop location with walk ability to schools and convenience stores. Schedule your visit today!
